CO2 intensity of electricity.source: Base year data from EIA State Electricity Data website, projected to 2050 using sales-weighted average trends in CO2 intensity for EMM regions that comprise a given state.

End-use electricity price.source: Base year data from EIA State Electricity Data website, projected to 2050 using sales-weighted average trends in residential & commercial electricity prices for EMM regions that comprise a given state; previous years (2016-2020) backfilled based on 2021 value from AEO 2022
